com.amplifyframework.storage

Class StorageCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.core.category.Category<StoragePlugin<?>>
      • com.amplifyframework.storage.StorageCategory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CategoryTypeable, StorageCategoryBehavior

    public final class StorageCategory
extends Category<StoragePlugin<?>>
implements StorageCategoryBehavior
    Defines the Client API consumed by the application. Internally routes the calls to the Storage Category plugins registered.
